reviews.text:
Suddenly, lights are off due to trouble, then they keep wait us more than 30min. It's over 9:30pm so all of restaurant's last order is finished.
Finally, they couldn't serve us and don't apologies, guarantees. Incredible staff attitude.
I suggest you that don't go this restaurant.
Love their shrimp based soup and the slightly chewy noodle texture. Prefer the original prawn and salt based one than the pork bone soup added or miso ones. Good view too.
Limited choices on menu but there is no need to offer many types of food at Ramen Noodle shop. Good Japanese noodle with flavor of shrimp. Crowded during weekends.

Very unique shrimp base soup ramen with "bouncy" noodles. Be aware that soup is oily and salty so might not be to the liking of some. Beautiful view of the HK skyline if you managed to get a window seat.
Clean, neat environment. Is special if having the Seaview seat. The noodle prawn soup base is very good, although bit salty which is normal for Japanese ramen.

result.name: 一幻拉麵

reviews.text: 拉麵好好味，少有蝦味湯底，正常價錢88蚊一碗，有半隻蛋兩塊肉，我加埋麵底15蚊，好飽。下次會試香港限定伴麵
很香濃的蝦湯味。個人較喜歡湯麵，味道豐富，既有蝦味，又有豬骨湯味。味道有點過濃。
地方寬敞，多座位，鋪排很好，拉麵價錢相宜，蝦湯伴著炸蝦乾、味道很香甜；而尖沙咀分店獨有的伴麵（攪清楚，不是沾麵，像越式撈麵，不過這麵已浸在濃湯裡），將麵和配料跟湯攪勻，就能吃了，味道是出奇的好味…不過我還是愛吃沾麵，但這種嘗試也很不錯呢！（7/6/2019更新）D膠杯用耐咗好多都好花，好似有積咁，睇見都唔想用，扣一星！

Suddenly, lights are off due to trouble, then they keep wait us more than 30min. It's over 9:30pm so all of restaurant's last order is finished.
Finally, they couldn't serve us and don't apologies, guarantees. Incredible staff attitude.
I suggest you that don't go this restaurant.
雖然好食，但無冷氣唔出聲，一路食，一路爆汗

result.name: Green Common Harbour City

reviews.text:
Really good, but no set lunch in this branch. 

A little bit expensive compare with other branches. Need 10% service charge. Restaurant location is very good, And it is always crowded. 

New dishes always added to the menu, customer will not feel repeating even visit every single week.

Food is delicious. free drinking water is supplied , staff are polite and helpful. 

Highly recommended for vegetarian.

The fusion and trendy restaurant is the very first of its type vegetarian in Harbour City. It serves innovated western, Japanese and Asian dishes. The receipt of bill can be redeemed some cash for immediate shopping in retail section for snacks, drinks, accessories and etc. 

Highly recommended for the vegetarians among thousands of dining options in different phrases of shopping mall.

Awesome that a place like this exists. The beyond meat burger was great. Texture similar to meat, made of pea protein, endorsed by Leonardo DiCaprio! 

Restaurant is in the mall section where all the kids clothes are. Ground floor. If you enter via canton rd to need to walk about 5 mins to another section of the mall. You cross over on level 2 around Chanel and Louis vuitton
Good flavors. However, the kitchen doesn't open till noon even though the store opens at 11:30.

Deceptive about their closing times. Please put your "last order" as your closing time. You're not the first Hong Kong restaurant to deceive people and to make people go all the way to your store only to find out that it's "last order".

一個玩手機半個鐘，1個廢青職員瞓覺，收銀紮辮麻甩佬問佢嘢反應遲鈍，叫佢地介紹佢地on 99
 星期6下午都咁！！！！

我食素20年，唔出街食嘢，冇煎炸所以好清淡，
110元嘅乜都有餐，蛋入口怪，腸有化學味，過咗半個鐘未散，
食完好滯，飲茶都散唔到，各位小心！
